P.append(passage("j8_urban_001",
    "The Night Shift City", "夜班城市", 8,
    "凌晨三点的城市并不像人们想象的那样安静。它只是换了一套运行系统。便利店的灯光在空无一人的街道上投下方形的白色光斑，店员靠在柜台上翻看手机，关东煮的汤还在冒着细密的蒸汽。环卫工人推着橘色的手推车沿固定路线移动，他们的路线图与白天的交通网络完全重合，只是行驶在上面的不再是汽车而是扫帚。出租车司机在固定的路口停靠等客，车内的暖光从侧窗透出来，远远看去像一串低垂的灯笼。医院急诊室是这座夜间城市唯一灯火通明的公共空间，它二十四小时运转，对时间的划分方式与普通人截然不同。我在这个城市生活了十五年，却是在开始上夜班之后才真正认识了它。白天的城市属于效率、竞争和社交规则，而夜班城市属于另一群人——他们维持着城市运转的基本底线，却几乎不被看见。当你清晨醒来看到干净的街道时，那并不是自然的状态，而是有人在你睡着的时候替你完成的。",
    "Língchén sān diǎn de chéngshì bìng bú xiàng rénmen xiǎngxiàng de nàyàng ānjìng. Tā zhǐshì huàn le yī tào yùnxíng xìtǒng. Biànlìdiàn de dēngguāng zài kōng wú yī rén de jiēdào shàng tóu xià fāngxíng de báisè guāngbān, diànyuán kào zài guìtái shàng fānkàn shǒujī, guāndōngzhǔ de tāng hái zài mào zhe xìmì de zhēngqì. Huánwèi gōngrén tuī zhe júsè de shǒutuīchē yán gùdìng lùxiàn yídòng, tāmen de lùxiàntú yǔ báitiān de jiāotōng wǎngluò wánquán chónghé, zhǐshì xíngshǐ zài shàngmiàn de bú zài shì qìchē ér shì sàozhou. Chūzūchē sījī zài gùdìng de lùkǒu tíngkào děng kè, chē nèi de nuǎn guāng cóng cèchuāng tòu chūlái, yuǎnyuǎn kàn qù xiàng yī chuàn dī chuí de dēnglóng. Yīyuàn jízhěnshì shì zhè zuò yèjiān chéngshì wéiyī dēnghuǒ tōngmíng de gōnggòng kōngjiān, tā èrshísì xiǎoshí yùnzhuǎn, duì shíjiān de huàfēn fāngshì yǔ pǔtōng rén jiérán bùtóng. Wǒ zài zhège chéngshì shēnghuó le shíwǔ nián, què shì zài kāishǐ shàng yèbān zhīhòu cái zhēnzhèng rènshi le tā. Báitiān de chéngshì shǔyú xiàolǜ, jìngzhēng hé shèjiāo guīzé, ér yèbān chéngshì shǔyú lìng yī qún rén——tāmen wéichí zhe chéngshì yùnzhuǎn de jīběn dǐxiàn, què jīhū bú bèi kànjiàn. Dāng nǐ qīngchén xǐnglái kàn dào gānjìng de jiēdào shí, nà bìng bú shì zìrán de zhuàngtài, ér shì yǒu rén zài nǐ shuìzháo de shíhou tì nǐ wánchéng de.",
    "The city at three in the morning is not as quiet as people imagine. It has merely switched to a different operating system. Convenience store lights cast square white patches on deserted streets, the clerk leans against the counter scrolling a phone, and the oden soup still sends up fine wisps of steam. Sanitation workers push orange carts along fixed routes—their maps overlap perfectly with the daytime traffic network, only now what travels the roads is brooms, not cars. Taxi drivers park at designated intersections waiting for fares, warm light seeping through side windows, looking from afar like low-hanging lanterns. The hospital emergency room is the only brightly lit public space in this nocturnal city, running twenty-four hours with a way of dividing time entirely unlike ordinary people's. I lived in this city for fifteen years, yet truly came to know it only after starting night shifts. The daytime city belongs to efficiency, competition, and social rules, while the night-shift city belongs to another group—those who maintain the basic floor of urban functioning yet are almost never seen. When you wake to clean streets in the morning, that is not a natural state; someone completed it for you while you slept.",
    mc("作者说城市在凌晨「换了一套运行系统」，这意味着什么？",
       "What does 'switching to a different operating system' mean?",
       [o("城市的基础设施在夜间进行维修","chéngshì de jīchǔ shèshī zài yèjiān jìnxíng wéixiū","Infrastructure undergoes maintenance at night"),
        o("城市由不同的人群以不同的逻辑在维持运转","chéngshì yóu bùtóng de rénqún yǐ bùtóng de luójí zài wéichí yùnzhuǎn","The city is kept running by different people with different logic",True),
        o("夜间的电脑系统与白天不同","yèjiān de diànnǎo xìtǒng yǔ báitiān bùtóng","Nighttime computer systems differ from daytime"),
        o("城市在夜间完全停止运作","chéngshì zài yèjiān wánquán tíngzhǐ yùnzuò","The city completely stops at night")], 0.45),
    mc("作者对夜班工作者的态度可以概括为：",
       "The author's attitude toward night-shift workers is:",
       [o("同情他们的辛苦并呼吁改善待遇","tóngqíng tāmen de xīnkǔ bìng hūyù gǎishàn dàiyù","Sympathy and calling for better treatment"),
        o("敬意与反思——他们维持城市运转却不被看见","jìngyì yǔ fǎnsī——tāmen wéichí chéngshì yùnzhuǎn què bú bèi kànjiàn","Respect and reflection—they maintain the city yet go unseen",True),
        o("羡慕夜班生活的自由","xiànmù yèbān shēnghuó de zìyóu","Envying the freedom of night-shift life"),
        o("客观记录，不带任何情感","kèguān jìlù, bú dài rènhé qínggǎn","Objective recording without emotion")], 0.5),
    mc("文末「那并不是自然的状态」的深层含义是：",
       "The deeper meaning of 'that is not a natural state' is:",
       [o("城市清洁需要使用化学物质","chéngshì qīngjié xūyào shǐyòng huàxué wùzhì","City cleaning requires chemicals"),
        o("街道本来就不会脏","jiēdào běnlái jiù bú huì zāng","Streets wouldn't get dirty naturally"),
        o("我们习以为常的整洁背后有隐形劳动者的付出","wǒmen xí yǐ wéi cháng de zhěngjié bèihòu yǒu yǐnxíng láodòngzhě de fùchū","Behind the cleanliness we take for granted is invisible laborers' effort",True),
        o("自然界本身是混乱的","zìránjiè běnshēn shì hùnluàn de","Nature itself is chaotic")], 0.45)))

